      "content": "i feel like i'm just being told \"no\" without any real explanation. if i really wanted to go this route, what would be a safe way to do it? like, if i started taking maybe 3000mg of garlic extract a day and making sure i had a big kale smoothie every morning, would that be enough to manage it without the warfarin? i just need to know if there is a way to make this work naturally.",
